The evidence with the title 'Chain e-mail of obama "firsts" analyzed | barnson.org ' says Oct 25, 2012  ... First president to keep a dog trainer on retainer for $ 102,000 a year at taxpayer expense . FALSE. The now-deceased dog trainer who trained the Obamas' dog earned a total of $ 102,000 per year training many dogs for high-profile figures. US taxpayers do not pay $ 102,000 / year to a dogtrainer.
